EmailTemplate.name: All New Accounts - Virtual Training
EmailTemplate.subject: FREE VinSolutions Online Virtual Training
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Good Day,
Thank you for your time in discussing your VinSolutions account. I want to help make your transition as easy as possible. We have found that our most successful dealers complete full online training prior to onsite training. The Live Sessions run every business day and the Recorded Sessions can be accessed at any time. Your team is welcome to register for any classes they might need.
All Courses are available online and they can be completed from the dealership or anywhere an internet connection is available. If you have any questions about VinSolutions University and any of our certification levels, please feel free to ask. There are over 20 classes available to you. Here are a few I recommend for the different access levels.
Salesman Level Access: Sales 1, Sales 2, Sales 3, Mobile MotoSnap & Distribution
Manager Level Access: Manager 1, Manager 2, Inventory & Market Pricing Tool, Desking, Trade Appraisal and ILM/CRM Reporting
Admin Level Access: Admin Templates, Admin Sales Processes, Admin Desking Settings, Admin 1, Admin 2, Admin 3 and Admin CRS Surveys
Click Here for the Virtual Training Schedule
Click Here to access on-Demand Desking Training **All fields must be completed in order to receive credit for the course.
And don't forget there are pre-recorded classes too!
Thank You,
{!User.Name} {!User.Title} VinSolutions O: {!User.Phone} x {!User.Extension} F: 913-825-6396
